    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors not assessed, representing epistemic gaps. The overall credibility evidence package is accepted as complete for submission purposes, with the understanding that all identified gaps must be addressed prior to regulatory submission. No supplementary uncertainty quantification documentation was attached to individual validation results.",
